net.dgen.apitools
Class ItemDefinitionSync

java.lang.Object
  net.dgen.apitools.ItemDefinitionSync

public class ItemDefinitionSync
extends java.lang.Object

Class sync'ing ItemDefinition object with an item def on API. This class can create an item definition in AMEE. to do: compare ItemDefintion with one in AMEE and update item values and alg in AMEE accordingly.
